; Fields:
; 3ds_reticle_size - reticle size multiplier
; 3ds_shadow_project - distance from scope lens to projected shadow, in other words, eye relief
; 3ds_ffp_min_zoom - for FFP scopes, minimal magnification FOV
; 3ds_type - custom type, see description
; ms_count - number of different marks (should be supported by custom type)
; ms_colors - list of colors for illumination
;
; Custom types:
; 3ds_type = 1 - NV scope (nightvision shader is applied to main image)
; 3ds_type = 2 - 1P59 Giperon scope (red channel at first focal plane, green channel at second focal plane, blue channel rotated by zoom), has LED illumination
; 3ds_type = 3 - ACOG, sun illuminated scope (red channel is regular black reticle, green channel is illuminated area, blue channel is gray text)
; 3ds_type = 4 - LED illuminated scope
; 3ds_type = 5 - Masked LED illuminated scope (red channel is regular black reticle, green channel is illuminated area)
; 3ds_type = 6 - PKA ssetting to get rid of awful pip. The scope is too narrow to turn it into a proper red dot
;
; Use this ltx to modify scope parameters and universal magnification. Magnification can also be set in weapon section for guns with integrated scopes.

